<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>V. T. Kappu</author>
<hymn_number>209</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pielgal ka ngai ka Lal lenna,
 Lungkham umlohna gam nuom chu;
 Bangtik leh ka tung dem?
 Ka lungkhamna mitthi hi,
 Bangtik leh a hul dem, tia ka ngaihtuoh in,
 Ka ngaih Lalpa'n eihung puiin.

[V2]
 Hinna thingbak lim nuoi achun,
 Keile ei chawlhsak in Lalpa;
 Thepna chung sunni ka thuok zo puoi,
 Hinna thing bak lim nuoi achun,
 Kei le ei chawlhsak in Lalpa.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel dahum thuok zote chu,
 A chungah puon In Na zakmaw?
 Keile ei zak khum in,
 Chawlhna mun nuom a um puoi;
 Khawvel gamthip ahin, chawlhna ka deih vangin,
 Thepna sunnipi a sa ie !

[V4]
 3. Zie khawvel gamgaw laka hin,
 Chawlhna um dingin ka ngai a;
 Chawlhna ding la umlo,
 Chen den theihna la umlo,
 Khawvel dahum ahi tih ka hetdawk phetin,
 Ka ngai ie Hinna Thing limnuoi.

[V5]
 4. Aw Hinna Thing lim nuoi a chun,
 Mi thiengthote a chawl zotau;
 Kei hi bangti ka him?
 Chawl theilo ka um hi;
 Ka taksa hin ei nang hei lamdan ni tungleh,
 Keile kichawl tang ka ting aw !</lyrics>
<title>Hinna Thingbak Li'm !</title>
</song>